Kate Lester https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kate_Lester 0 Kate Lester (born Sarah Cody, 12 June 1857 – 12 October 1924) was an English theatrical and silent film actress. Her family, the Suydams of New York, were staying in Britain at the time of her birth.
